name: MultiValueMap_containsValueTest
description: Unit tests for the containsValue method in the MultiValueMap class.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValuePresentInCollection
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value present in the collection.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValueNotPresentInCollection
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value not present in the collection.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_EmptyMap
test_cases.description: Tests the containsValue method on an empty map.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_NullValue
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly handles a null value.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_MultipleKeysWithSameValue
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value present under multiple keys.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValuePresentInDifferentCollections
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies values present in different collections.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValueRemovedFromCollection
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value after it has been removed from a collection.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValueAddedToNewCollection
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value added to a new collection.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValueAddedToExistingCollection
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value added to an existing collection.

test_cases.name: testContainsValue_ValueRemovedFromAllCollections
test_cases.description: Tests if the containsValue method correctly identifies a value after it has been removed from all collections.
